headline.main: Exclusive: Pentagon's Budget Plan Funds 404 Lockheed F-35 Jets-Sources
headline.print_headline: Exclusive: Pentagon's Budget Plan Funds 404 Lockheed F-35 Jets-Sources

docs.snippet: The U.S. Defense Department plans to buy 404 Lockheed Martin Corp F-35 fighter jets over the next five years, a net decrease of 5 to 7 percent from last year's plan, sources familiar with the plans said on Friday....
docs.lead_paragraph: The U.S. Defense Department plans to buy 404 Lockheed Martin Corp F-35 fighter jets over the next five years, a net decrease of 5 to 7 percent from last year's plan, sources familiar with the plans said on Friday.
